Lynk delivers a seamless and convenient digital banking experience that allows you to leave local bank limits behind. We believe in the power of digital and promote the efficiency of online financial operations that make the daily life of our customers simpler.

What do you get with a Lynk corporate account?

International money operations, including SWIFT and SEPA transfers, with a unique European IBAN. Visa and Mastercard cards for optimal management of corporate funds.Foreign exchange at competitive rates. An app for activity overview and total control over your money 24/7.

The Lynk app gives you access to an entire range of essential financial operations. You will be able to send and receive money, view the transaction history, get in touch with our customer support, top up your card, and so much more. It is the ultimate tool for money management at the tap of a finger.

What do you get with a Lynk personal account?

International transfers with a unique European IBAN. Foreign exchange at competitive rates. Mastercard and Visa cards for seamless payments and ATM withdrawals at pretty-much any location in the world. An app for activity overview and complete control over your money 24/7.

The Lynk app features:
– Access your funds 24/7;
– International and domestic transfer execution;
– Real-time push notifications about the operations;
– Currency exchange at competitive rates;
– Mastercard and Visa cards;
– Instant card top-up;
– Mass payout initiation.

With Lynk, you will enjoy:
– Fast & remote account opening;
– Competitive, fair fees;
– Transparency, security, and compliance with financial regulations;
– Professional customer support;
– 24/7 operation.

